channel.description:
Drew Scape Project is now recruiting! Join today! I am working with Chemical to help me with my server and client. I did release my Java in Lava client wich is found in the download section. I am trying to also make a built in Server into the client. We are trying to get the most updated items from RuneScape. We have so far made the following items...
1. Dragon Full Helm 2. Lunar Staff 3. Skill Capes + Emotes 4. Skill Hoods and Capes (e.g. Farming Cape and Hood) 5. New Dragon Fire Shield (grabbed from Silabs client) 6. Dragon Boots
So join us today and remember to also join our forums here [font=Verdana][url=http:\\www.drewscape.smfforfree3]Here[/font] ~~Drew~~
